{
  "stem": "21919.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We knew that it was a she, that she was clever, because when it was 11 o'clock, she would come to school and spend the 15 minutes with me at recess and then go back home.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But during the war, the Germans took her away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she ran away from them and came home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when she would smell or hear or-- or sense that the Germans were coming, she would run up to the top floor on-- on a ladder, which is very unusual for a dog to do, and a big dog at that.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But she knew that she had to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we found out how clever she was during the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then they-- they took her away again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know if-- of they kept her or shot her or whatever they did with her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we didn't have her anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first tragedy in our family was when the first bomb fell, the first German bomb.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was when they start the war with Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were divided.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our city became Russian in '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And just a few kilometers away was the river that divided the Russian border with the German border.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bug.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "B-O-G.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember it was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what I thought was thunder was the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the first bomb fell not far from our house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it hit-- hit one of our cousins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is when-- because families were so close, we found out immediately that he was in the hospital, and he was hurt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was the only son of my mother's first cousin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this was the first time that I realized everybody was crying and everybody was upset about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
